    "However, accurate co-registration is likely challenging in the case of highly distorted images.Previously, SR has been used to increase MRI quality for the knee by Chaudhari et al.",
    "The authors thoroughly evaluate the performance of the SR method for visualizing cartilage morphometry and osteophytes.",
